{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act43side", "eventName": "紅絲絨", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "AD-ST-2", "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "焦點", "storyInfo": "兇手不加掩飾的暴行鬧得片場人心惶惶。格蕾塔以自己的經歷告訴眾人她的眼光值得信任，隨後解散了劇組——所有人都能自行選擇，她會跟想繼續拍攝的人完成作品。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "62_g3_filmset", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$darkness_03_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1845_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1847_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喂喂，你也看到邁克爾和瑪麗昂的屍體了，對吧？", "name": "工作人員A"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎喲，我好不容易才把那個恐怖的景象甩出腦海，你怎麼又再說了！", "name": "工作人員B"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我、我的手都在抖，感覺快要握不住錄音桿了……", "name": "工作人員B"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你怎麼還想著工作！我們現在待的地方真的有一個連環殺人魔！", "name": "工作人員A"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我們快點逃走吧？", "name": "工作人員B"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "逃？你忘了邁克爾和瑪麗昂是為什麼被兇手盯上的嗎？", "name": "工作人員A"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "邁克爾的腳下還放著行李，聽說他做了充足的準備，找到了私下開溜的方法……", "name": "工作人員A"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但他還是在離開這個地塊的前一刻被抓到了。", "name": "工作人員A"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個兇手不會讓任何人離開的。", "name": "工作人員A"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就像《開膛黎博利傑克》一樣，這裡是他的獵場，我們每個人都可能是他的獵物。", "name": "工作人員A"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1843_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "focus": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿布納，你有多久沒檢查過胸架了？", "name": "攝影助理"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你看，升降設備這邊的幾個螺絲都已經鬆了，一個不小心，攝影機就會整個摔在地上……", "name": "攝影助理"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "focus": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1843_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "摔到就摔到。", "name": "阿布納"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "focus": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我幫你保養一下這幾組鏡頭吧。", "name": "攝影助理"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "focus": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1843_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不用。", "name": "阿布納"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "focus": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我是你的助理，阿布納。", "name": "攝影助理"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "focus": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1843_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別以為我不知道你獻殷勤是為了什麼——滾遠一點，小子。", "name": "阿布納"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "focus": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "道爾頓的死不是意外，對不對？還有謝莉、邁克爾和瑪麗昂……", "name": "攝影助理"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "兇手不可能是無差別殺人，所有的受害者，都和五年前的那起意外有關。", "name": "攝影助理"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "focus": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1843_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你應該去當娛樂記者，而不是攝影助理。", "name": "阿布納"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "focus": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也不衝突啊，前者更好賺錢……阿布納，我親愛的阿布納，五年前你也在，反正現在有時間，你就跟我說一下嘛！", "name": "攝影助理"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1835_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1830_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1835_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "米蘭妮女士，現在還沒有您的戲……", "name": "斯蒂芬"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1830_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我難道能放心繼續在房間裡研究“杜邦夫人”死前的妝髮造型？", "name": "米蘭妮"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1835_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這關係到結尾那幾場高潮戲，抱歉，我還沒有……", "name": "斯蒂芬"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1830_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，你的神遲到了。但我現在沒有心情責怪你和你的神，親愛的。", "name": "米蘭妮"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "發生了這麼大的事，如果不是離主城區太遠，藍卡塢的警察現在已經封鎖整個地塊，這部片也早就停工了……", "name": "米蘭妮"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，現在的情況也沒有多好。", "name": "米蘭妮"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1830_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斯蒂芬，我開始擔心自己的投資要血本無歸了。", "name": "米蘭妮"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這幾天發生的事情，你知道多少隱情？格蕾塔知道多少？", "name": "米蘭妮"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1835_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "斯蒂芬"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1845_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斯蒂芬導演、米蘭妮女士，原來兩位也在啊。", "name": "工作人員C"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1845_1#1$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crwddiscuss_outside", "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs", "volume": 0.0}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.7, "channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "製片人呢？格蕾塔應該給所有人一個交代！", "name": "工作人員C"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1845_1#1$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#5$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#5$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "竊竊私語。"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "到處都是竊竊私語的聲音，整個攝影棚內，沒有一個人在工作。"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "三起命案、四個死者，接二連三的變故摧毀了這些人的狀態，恐慌、憤怒、困惑、無所適從……整個劇組在失控的邊緣。"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真吵啊，吵得令人心煩意亂。她討厭這種感覺。"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_spotlight", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "格蕾塔徑直走向攝影棚的中央，她打開了最亮的那盞場燈，刺目的光亮頓時打斷了所有人的動作與談話，人們注意到了她。"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "格蕾塔深深呼吸。"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$ponder_intro", "key": "$ponder_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "各位，我要宣布一些事情。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不是演員，台詞功底沒有那麼好，聽不清楚的就再靠過來一點。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_footsteps_flock", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "米蘭妮"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "斯蒂芬"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "阿布納"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "工作人員們"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crwddiscuss_outside", "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs", "volume": 0.0}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.3, "channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幾分鐘後，各位可以確認自己在藍卡塢的專屬金融終端。來之前，我之前已經交代會計，付清了劇組每一位成員的尾款。", "name": "格蕾塔"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，道爾頓、謝莉、邁克爾、瑪麗昂，除了為這幾位朋友結算應得的酬勞之外，還會給他們的家屬發放撫恤金，我事後會專門處理。", "name": "格蕾塔"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，《杜邦夫人之死》的拍攝還沒有結束，合約還有效力，我本不需要這麼做——但畢竟，已經沒有幾個人還有心思繼續工作了。", "name": "格蕾塔"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1830_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘿，格蕾塔，這不像你。", "name": "米蘭妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1830_1#1$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "劇組只不過是出了一些……不算小的意外，還沒到放棄的時候。", "name": "米蘭妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1830_1#1$1"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還是說，經歷這些事情之後，身為製片人，你已經對電影最後的品質不抱任何期待了。", "name": "米蘭妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1830_1#1$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放棄？親愛的，你想多了。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#1$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我從不懷疑自己的眼光，當然也談不上會放棄。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#1$1"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1830_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是你現在……", "name": "米蘭妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1830_1#3$1"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我講一個故事給大家聽吧。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#1$1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喂，小子……", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#1$1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "格蕾塔女士，請問您在叫我嗎？", "name": "攝影助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#6$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拿出你的錄音筆、筆記本、速記終端……隨便什麼，然後坐好，用心聽。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#1$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什、什麼意思？", "name": "攝影助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#6$1"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別再讓我看到你那些偷偷摸摸的小動作，我接下來說的所有事情，你都可以光明正大地記下來。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你也可以去找《特里蒙娛樂週刊》、《藍卡塢咖啡時間》、《多面人物》……我不會用任何方式追究你的責任，只要你能把消息帶出去。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論對你來說，出賣消息換取的是獎賞，還是，懲罰。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "攝影助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“藍卡塢學院獎”，想必在場的每一個人都很熟悉。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "藍卡塢面向新人的專業獎項，每年都有無數的影視學院學生、電影愛好者向它投遞稿件，想盡辦法證明自己多麼懂創作多麼懂市場。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們渴望作品能入選，因為哪怕只是拿到最小的獎項，也代表自己得到了進入藍卡塢的資格……有個斐迪亞也不例外。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她自認眼光不凡，有想法也有毅力，自信地認為哪怕暫時只能擠在租屋處，最後也會站在藍卡塢發布會的紅毯上。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "終於，她等來了最好的故事，找到了最好的搭檔，她聚集團隊，把那個故事拍了出來，寄了出去。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#1$1"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但這個來自小鄉村的傢伙太渴望自己能成功了，更何況此刻身上還背負著所有同伴的信任……", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "評選結束的倒數計時越近，她的渴望越強，對自己作品的懷疑反而越深。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她也搞不懂自己怎麼會動那種歪心思，她求遍親友，湊了一筆鉅款——對當時的她來說是個不小的數目……然後，她敲開了那些評審的門。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#8$1"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼聽起來這麼熟悉……", "name": "攝影助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#6$1"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“學院獎”揭曉的當天，主辦單位公開了斐迪亞的所作所為，向全泰拉的觀眾證明了藍卡塢的專業與透明。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而那個斐迪亞呢？她投稿的作品被取消比賽資格，團隊的所有成員與她決裂，她失去了一切。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#4$1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想起來了！", "name": "攝影助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#3$1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這件事超級諷刺！根據主辦單位後來披露的資料……那個作品本來已經拿到了最高票，是最受評審們矚目的作品。", "name": "攝影助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "後來，那個傢伙用了十年的時間，窮盡所有辦法才重回藍卡塢，慢慢地，也做出了一點成績。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#7$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，她還幫自己改名了……格蕾塔·斯通。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#9$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "攝影助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "米蘭妮，現在你知道了吧？我是個極其愚蠢的人。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#4$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我主動向命運討要了一個玩笑。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#4$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幸好，這段聽起來連自己都倍感荒唐的經歷教會了我一件事——我不該懷疑自己。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我相信我自己的眼光，我不會放棄我想做的任何事情。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1830_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，你比我想像中的還有趣呢。", "name": "米蘭妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1830_1#2$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說實話，我一直以為你身上那股自以為是的感覺，是故意裝出來嚇人的。", "name": "米蘭妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1830_1#2$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1843_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "算了吧，格蕾塔。", "name": "阿布納"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1843_1#1$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你突然搞這麼一齣，又開始說這個沒頭沒尾的故事，不就是為了博取我們的同情……", "name": "阿布納"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1843_1#1$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們站的地方有人死了，我們的前面有天災……發生了這麼多的事，你還想讓我們繼續為你賣命？", "name": "阿布納"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1843_1#1$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道你一直對我耿耿於懷，阿布納。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……從五年前開始。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1843_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我才不敢呢。畢竟我當年就是靠著那部電影裡的經典鏡頭，拿到了藍卡塢最佳攝影獎……", "name": "阿布納"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1843_1#1$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是一個電影攝影師能拿到的最高榮譽……是你賞賜給我的！", "name": "阿布納"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1843_1#1$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但在那之後呢？", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "明明達到了職業生涯的巔峰，卻自暴自棄，短短半年後就沒人敢再請你掌鏡。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#5$1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "曾經你那麼疼愛自己手中的攝影機，如今卻像對待空空的洋芋片袋子一樣對待它們……", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#5$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "進《杜邦夫人之死》這個劇組之前，你甚至在賭場裡輸掉了跟了自己十幾年的老夥伴，對吧？", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#5$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1843_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "阿布納"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1843_1#7$1"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你憎恨五年前的那部電影，你憎恨那個讓你獲獎的畫面，你憎恨當時讓你把它保留下來的我——", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#5$1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1843_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒錯！", "name": "阿布納"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1843_1#4$1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的攝影機偶然拍下了那個叫勞拉的女孩從高空墜落的畫面，我當時看到你的表情時就知道你不懷好意……", "name": "阿布納"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1843_1#4$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我警告過你很多次，但你還是硬把那個畫面剪到了電影裡……", "name": "阿布納"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1843_1#4$1"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1843_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "影評人們越是誇那個鏡頭多麼真實多麼震撼，我就越覺得可笑！", "name": "阿布納"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1843_1#8$1"}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "電影是造夢的藝術，攝影機是造夢的手和看夢的眼睛，你侮辱了那個女孩子，你侮辱了我！", "name": "阿布納"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1843_1#8$1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1843_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我討厭我手裡的這些機器，我討厭我的工作，你懂嗎？", "name": "阿布納"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1843_1#4$1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿布納，既然如此，放下它。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1843_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你說什麼？", "name": "阿布納"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1843_1#3$1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不好意思，我們有點離題了，讓我們言歸正傳——", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "確認酬勞到帳後，各位可以隨時離開劇組。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "想要儘快逃離這個危險重重的地塊的，請自便；害怕連環殺人犯想要找個地方躲一下的，請自便……", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為種種目的想要當偵探的，請自便；甚至那個還不願意放棄復仇的兇手，也請自便。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "《杜邦夫人之死》絕大多數的拍攝工作已經完成，只剩下最後這兩天，只剩下最後幾場高潮戲……", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還願意留下來的人，或許我們依然可以把它拍完。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至於缺少的攝影師……我會接手阿布納的工作。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1843_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "阿布納"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1843_1#2$1"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "攝影助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "米蘭妮？", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#1$1"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "畢竟我沒辦法臨時變出另一個“杜邦夫人”。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#1$1"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1830_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你知道的，我沒有選擇。", "name": "米蘭妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1830_1#1$1"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還想靠這部電影打敗瑪麗安娜呢，格蕾塔。", "name": "米蘭妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1830_1#1$1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "災難，難道不是另一種形式的眷顧嗎？", "name": "米蘭妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1830_1#1$1"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "瑪麗安娜已經息影多年了，真不知道你為什麼這麼執著於她。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#1$1"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1830_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這就不用你過問了。", "name": "米蘭妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1830_1#1$1"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但醜話說在前面，人都跑光之後，你在意的那些女主角的待遇、片場的規矩……恐怕也顧不了那麼多了。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#1$1"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1830_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈。", "name": "米蘭妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1830_1#1$1"}, {"id": 261, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斯蒂芬。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#1$1"}, {"id": 263, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1835_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道我知道，我會今天晚上就把結局修改出來！", "name": "斯蒂芬"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1835_1#2$1"}, {"id": 265, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我相信我拍下這個故事時的判斷，親愛的，這幾天，你也已經思考夠久、累積夠多經驗了。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#1$1"}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "天災近在咫尺，死亡就在眼前……你的神難道不愛這些素材嗎？", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#1$1"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1835_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "斯蒂芬"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1835_1#1$1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "感謝各位這段時間的付出，祝大家好運。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#1$1"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想說的就是這些。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#1$1"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_spotlightc", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}